  "text": "Mouth opening Prior to surgery, mouth opening will be assessed by the laser operator, using a caliper to measure the distance between the incisal edges of the upper and lower central incisors as described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
